{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1773436054212,"sessionID":"ses_316fcbe54ffegvIvV0T61c4er2","part":{"id":"prt_ce9069dae002YtiwhmCiQC1Vk2","sessionID":"ses_316fcbe54ffegvIvV0T61c4er2","messageID":"msg_ce9069561001ImGfzwd0PFBDCw","type":"tool","callID":"toolu_vrtx_01Mvi36AS7q5AeeQ55aK9Lda","tool":"bash","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"command":"git add src/index.ts && git commit -m \"fix(cli-bugs): simplify set-status/set-priority/set-difficulty routing in index.ts\n\nThe previous logic had unnecessarily nested conditionals that duplicated the\ncommand call in both if/else branches. When args.title was falsy but\nargs.featureId existed, the outer condition entered but the logic was correct\nonly by accident. Simplified to a single flat check: resolve the value from\neither the positional arg or the flag, then validate and call once.\"","description":"Commit index.ts routing fix"},"output":"[feature/cli-bugs 138efbb] fix(cli-bugs): simplify set-status/set-priority/set-difficulty routing in index.ts\n 1 file changed, 45 insertions(+), 78 deletions(-)\n","title":"Commit index.ts routing fix","metadata":{"output":"[feature/cli-bugs 138efbb] fix(cli-bugs): simplify set-status/set-priority/set-difficulty routing in index.ts\n 1 file changed, 45 insertions(+), 78 deletions(-)\n","exit":0,"description":"Commit index.ts routing fix","truncated":false},"time":{"start":1773436054202,"end":1773436054211}}}}
