{"type":"text","timestamp":1773436069512,"sessionID":"ses_316fcbe54ffegvIvV0T61c4er2","part":{"id":"prt_ce906d2ad002wKeVaVipbWphU1","sessionID":"ses_316fcbe54ffegvIvV0T61c4er2","messageID":"msg_ce906c979001FyZFfohLi4uGIn","type":"text","text":"### Bug 6: Fix completion.ts — wrong status values, missing toon format\n\nThe valid statuses from `task-schema.ts` are: `backlog`, `planned`, `in_progress`, `blocked`, `in_review`, `done`, `cancelled`. The completion scripts use: `ready in-progress done failed cancelled blocked` which is wrong. Also, `--output` should include `toon` alongside `text json`.","time":{"start":1773436069512,"end":1773436069512}}}
