{"type":"text","timestamp":1773436211419,"sessionID":"ses_316fcbe54ffegvIvV0T61c4er2","part":{"id":"prt_ce908e3e1001ZWFp3kUeJ4Q4qS","sessionID":"ses_316fcbe54ffegvIvV0T61c4er2","messageID":"msg_ce908dc0e001QJWcAsngd3pA9S","type":"text","text":"All 7 bugs fixed across 7 commits. Here's a summary of everything that was done:\n\n## Summary of Changes\n\nAll 8 identified bugs have been fixed across 7 commits on the `feature/cli-bugs` branch. Typecheck and build both pass cleanly.\n\n### Commits:\n\n1. **`ceb31c6`** — `abort.ts`: Added `return` statements after `outputError()` calls so TypeScript can properly narrow `state` (from `WaveState | null`) and `agent` (from `undefined`) types in subsequent code.\n\n2. **`9fa91b2`** — `retry.ts`: Replaced `config.tasksFile` (deprecated) with `config.tasksDir` in error message on line 95.\n\n3. **`bacacd1`** — `history.ts`: Added `return` after `outputError()` and removed the fragile `record!` non-null assertion, letting TypeScript properly narrow the type.\n\n4. **`138efbb`** — `index.ts` (routing): Simplified the `set-status`, `set-priority`, and `set-difficulty` cases from unnecessarily nested if/else with duplicated command calls into a single flat pattern: resolve the value from positional or flag, validate, call once. Reduced 78 lines to 45.\n\n5. **`b77bfc2`** — `completion.ts`: Fixed `--status` completions across all three shells (bash, zsh, fish) from wrong values (`ready in-progress done failed cancelled blocked`) to correct canonical values (`backlog planned in_progress blocked in_review done cancelled`). Added `toon` to `--output` completions.\n\n6. **`a01bc96`** — `index.ts` (validation): Added NaN validation for all 5 numeric CLI args (`--top-priority`, `--quickest-wins`, `--max-concurrent`, `--max-retries`, `--tail`). Previously, `--tail foo` would silently pass `NaN` through.\n\n7. **`eef8b8a`** — `prompt.ts` + `templates.ts`: Replaced 2 deprecated `config.tasksFile` references with `config.tasksDir` in prompt generation, and fixed a stale JSDoc comment in templates.ts.","time":{"start":1773436211418,"end":1773436211418}}}
